      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这个地图要覆盖整个学习曲线。我理解的起点是环境搭建，终点是高级控制算法。中间大概分几个阶段比较合适？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Robot PU JavaScript Tutorials"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我设想七大模块。第一块\"Setup & Basics\"，让新手能跑通第一个程序；然后直接进硬件和核心API；接着用音乐表达做第一个有趣的项目，这个阶段数学要求低，培养信心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Setup & Basics",
        "Music and Expression"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "低门槛入门，高粘性设计。那音乐模块后面接什么？直接上算法会不会太陡？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Music and Expression"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "音乐后面放\"Communication & Control\"，用radio做遥控和点对点聊天。学生能做出远程控制的机器人，成就感很强，而且只需要理解基本的通信概念。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Communication & Control",
        "radio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在地图上标出第三模块：Communication & Control，包含远程控制协议、手柄映射和点对点消息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Communication & Control",
